{"tid":2306310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［講定先］陰謀論 港共中共 黎緊復工復課條件就係全民監察","createTime":"2020-11-30T10:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T12:51:46.000Z","uid":44367,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"221272f55f1225e1c053029dec136b7f54e20e63","tid":2306310,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"先講結論 <br />\n<br />\n所謂第三波防疫操施目的 -立法會延期 -成功<br />\n<br />\n所謂第四波 目的-全民下載安心出行 健康碼 打中國疫苗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成功......？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎打左香港咁耐 七百萬每日一百人感染真係好嚴重？<br />\n<br />\n退一萬步講 中左武肺係咪真係要咁驚死？ <br />\n<br />\n由第一日開始 香港人從來唔信港共 四圍撲口罩 撲防疫物資  一個人口咁密集既城巿每日確診數先可以減到咁低 <br />\n <br />\n香港人防疫成功 幾時有靠過港共？<br />\n唔好再俾港共玩死自己 <br />\n<br />\n香港人係靠自己 唔係靠港共<br />\n<br />\n保持信念 無人郁得到你"},{"pid":"07195118460925ea1d4a548a727cc7eb6bee5a19","tid":2306310,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:52:50.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53343871dbeaa28f0bea2cec90e6f84f3ad48388","tid":2306310,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:54:21.000Z","msg":"我咪唔出去食飯囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3176422cdbf163976f09a7fd0a50f7a9e906ed","tid":2306310,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:56:30.000Z","msg":"Btw好多人等緊移民船"},{"pid":"8b6a3a954b3dd024648215e6343427c6a213da9c","tid":2306310,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces